Class DialogComponentDateRangeInput

  • public class DialogComponentDateRangeInput
extends AbstractDialogComponentRangeInput<DateInputPanel,SettingsModelDateRangeBounded,java.util.Date>
    A DialogComponent to input a data range via two date entry components. The range is bounded, with the bounds determined in the SettingsModelDateRangeBounded supplied
